{"tid":2510853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"石禮謙指入境處反駁審計報告違反政府協議 要求張建宗跟進","createTime":"2021-04-30T12:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T13:37:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd9cf78dc852f836afdc08830b6b2d5174a9d07","tid":2510853,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"立法會內務委員會下午開會，身兼政府帳目委員會主席的經民聯石禮謙，在會上提到入境處日前公開反駁審計報告事件，要求政務司司長張建宗跟進。<br />\n<br />\n石禮謙表示，政府在2020年2月曾發出公函，指任何審計署署長提交立法會的報告，政府部門都不應該發起任何公眾的辯論。石禮謙指入境處做法違反協議，提醒張建宗執行通函要求。<br />\n<br />\n審計署周三發表的審計報告批評入境處，調查假結婚個案進度緩慢，建議入境處加快處理未完結的調查個案。入境處發聲明反駁，指對於一些不懂刑事調查的人，胡亂批評執法部門的個案處理手法，處方深表遺憾。"},{"pid":"95ce10a32a9038975e749ffa7b295822f56c4498","tid":2510853,"uid":95221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"係咪要張建宗道歉？"},{"pid":"01a197475f3e8174f24b32848f34a429b2339fcb","tid":2510853,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95ce10a32a9038975e749ffa7b295822f56c4498","tid":2510853,"uid":95221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"係咪要張建宗道歉？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad85733bc6d372676591c226092c78702428f3f","tid":2510853,"uid":99872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"往死裏打"},{"pid":"297e181c652ce1b2cde5e3d8aa725e3534a2b725","tid":2510853,"uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"95ce10a32a9038975e749ffa7b295822f56c4498","tid":2510853,"uid":95221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"係咪要張建宗道歉？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ima